Pre-Game Insights: The Lithuanian national team will start a new cycle with a match against Cyprus launching the new Nations League season.
The match will be broadcast live on the LRT Plius channel.
The match at the Marijampolė stadium will begin at 7 PM.
Lithuania's head coach Edgaras Jankauskas commented on the transfer of the match from Kaunas to Marijampolė, expressing disappointment over the circumstances that led to the change.
